java.logic

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.logic.Controller

  • public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
    The Controller class keeps the current state of the game, as seen from the vantage point of this user. It also keeps track of information pertinent to this player, such as hosts and ports.
